IWD NO DBUS
-----------

GOALS

* Get the daemon to function using config files (No iwctl and friends). DONE

* Implement IPC between clients without DBUS. SOON(TM)


TODO

* Set up CI and build/test each commit automatically.
* Remove all DBUS related code from src/*. DONE
* TBA


BUILDING

    ./configure \
        --prefix=/usr \
        --localstatedir=/var

    make
    make install


SYSTEM-WIDE CONFIG (/etc/iwd/main.conf)

    [General]
    EnableNetworkConfiguration=true
    UseDefaultInterface=true

    [Network]
    NameResolvingService=resolvconf


PER-NETWORK CONFIGS (/var/lib/iwd/ssid.psk) (or use iwd_passphrase)

    [Security]
    Passphrase=password


SSID NAMING

See: IWD.NETWORK(5) (man iwd.network).

